Ashlee+Evan was a 2018 American reality television series on E! starring Ashlee Simpson and Evan Ross.[1][2] In 2019, Simpson stated in an interview with Us Weekly that the show would not be returning for a second season.[3]

Premise [ edit ]

Ashlee+Evan follows Ashlee Simpson and Evan Ross, son of Diana Ross, as they try to balance their lives as new parents and the pressures of living up to their famous family names.[4][5]
